DON'T DO SKINCARE ❌

🚫Don't do skincare if you cannot cleanse your face twice a day.

🚫Don't do skincare if you cannot Wear Sunscreen daily.

🚫Don't do skincare if you don't have the habit of washing your Pillowcase Frequently. 

🚫Don't do skincare if you cannot have a separate towel for face and body.

🚫Don't do skincare if you have the habit of taking bath in extremely hot Water.

🚫Don't do skincare if you cannot stop yourself from blindly following a trend.

🚫Don't do skincare if you cannot sleep early.

🚫Don't do skincare if you cannot stop your hands from touching your face constantly.

🚫Don't do skincare if you cannot stop yourself from blindly following random DIY.
